d_for_admission_in_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for admission in 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for admission in 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439165\">About the University of Stellenbosch SUN Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439166\"><strong>How to Apply for SUN Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439167\">Documents Required for SUN Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439168\">SUN Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439169\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80439170\">Applying for Financial Assistance<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80439171\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for admission in 2024?<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-university-of-stellenbosch-sun-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_University_of_Stellenbosch_SUN_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439165\"><\/a>About the University of Stellenbosch (SUN) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the University of Stellenbosch(SUN) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80439166\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for SUN Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/student.sun.ac.za\/signup\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/student.sun.ac.za\/signup<\/a> \u00a0<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-sun-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_SUN_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439167\"><\/a>Documents Required for SUN Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/www.sun.ac.za\/english\/maties\/Pages\/Apply-ApplicationDocuments.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view all required documents<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"sun-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"SUN_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439168\"><\/a>SUN Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R700<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/www.sun.ac.za\/english\/maties\/fees\/application-fee\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to see all application fees guidelines<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439169\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>Take Note of These Dates<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Undergraduate Programmes application closes <strong>6 April<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Applications open for financial assistance at Stellenbosch University on <strong>3 May<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Applications open for all postgraduate programmes on <strong>1 June<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Applications close for all undergraduate programmes on <strong>31 July<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Residence applications close on <strong>31 July<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Applications close for Stellenbo\u200bsch University financial assistance on <strong>31 August<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Applications close for Diploma in Public Accountability (Telematic Education) on <strong>15 December<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439170\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NAFS application portal<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.gov.za\/services\/tertiary-education\/apply-financial-assistance-national-student-financial-aid-scheme-nsfas\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-admission-in-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_admission_in_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80439171\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for admission in 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong> Only\u00a0<strong>School of Tomorrow\u00a0<\/strong>applicants and applicants to the<strong>\u00a0Faculty of Law.\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"The University of Stellenbosch Application for Admission 2024 intake, SUN Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status, Closing date&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1108,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1107"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1107"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1107\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1107"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1107"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1107"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}